channel.title: RSPS History (Family Tree)
channel.description:
Since I've seen a few threads and questions about this throughout the forum, I decided to make this a while ago. In attempt to recover all of the history on RSPS, I've asked a few veterans, but only got a few replies concerning the background of it. But here's my knowledge, all backed by veteran members and runewiki:
[center][IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/122oytw.png[/img][/center]
For a full, magnified image, look here: http://i39.tinypic.com/2exv8cm.png
If you have anything that could help the thread, or anything to fix or add, just post it here and I'll be sure to modify the image as long as you provide some form of proof that it is legitimate information.
